OL,3,C'Dangerous': People with allergies
OL,4,Cwarned not to eat Dubai-style chocolate
OL,6,FPeople with allergies have been warned
OL,7,Fnot to eat Dubai-style chocolate,
OL,8,Fafter a number of products failed to
OL,9,Fmeet UK food standards, the food
OL,10,Fsafety watchdog has warned.
OL,12,FThe Food Standards Agency (FSA) said
OL,13,Fit has found "several" of these
OL,14,Fproducts in the UK which have failed
OL,15,Fto meet safety and labelling
OL,16,Frequirements and warned that it would
OL,17,Fbe "dangerous" for consumers with
OL,18,Fallergies to eat the bars.
