OL,3,C'Dangerous': People with allergies
OL,4,Cwarned not to eat Dubai-style chocolate
OL,6,FThe chocolate products, which
OL,7,Ftypically contain a filling made of
OL,8,Fpistachio, tahini and shredded filo
OL,9,Fpastry, have soared in popularity over
OL,10,Fthe past year.
OL,12,FThe watchdog said it is reviewing
OL,13,Fsampling data from products currently
OL,14,Fon sale to check whether they meet
OL,15,Ffood safety standards.
OL,17,FRebecca Sudworth, director of policy
OL,18,Fat the FSA said "we've found that some
OL,19,Fproducts contain peanut and sesame
OL,20,Fthat aren't declared on the label".
