OL,11,FThe watchdog added that it is advising
OL,12,Fconsumers with allergies to avoid the
OL,13,FDubai-style chocolate as a precaution
OL,14,Funtil its full results are known.
OL,16,FMs Sudworth said: "If you're buying a
OL,17,Fgift for someone who lives with
OL,18,Fallergies, our advice is to avoid
OL,19,Fbuying these products. This includes
OL,20,Fall allergies, not just peanut and
OL,21,Fsesame.
