OL,6,F"People without allergies can consume
OL,7,Fthese products, especially where they
OL,8,Fare supplied by reputable brands and
OL,9,Fretailers."
OL,11,FJessica Merryfield, head of policy and
OL,12,Fcampaigns at the Chartered Trading
OL,13,FStandards Institute (CTSI), said: "The
OL,14,Flegal requirements on this are clear `
OL,15,Fany food containing allergens needs to
OL,16,Fbe clearly identified and labelled as
OL,17,Fsuch to allow consumers to make
OL,18,Finformed and safe choices.
